Layer 7: Reflection Layer

Returns the model to the user in a useful way.

This is critical.

The system should not only optimize recommendation.
It should also enable self-recognition.

Reflection outputs
	•	“You choose protectors more than performers.”
	•	“You prefer symbols of loyalty over symbols of beauty.”
	•	“Your taste clusters around earned strength, not polished dominance.”
	•	“Your picks show a bias toward redemption stories and misunderstood figures.”

This makes the engine a self-discovery instrument rather than only an ad tool.

